    "title": "Restart IBD after import/reindex finishes",
    "body": "After a reindex or import, no special code exists to force an IBD to be started. So if by the time that happens, you're already connected to max number of peers, IBD is only started when a new block is announced somewhere.\n\nMuch more complete solutions for the block download management are necessary, but this subproblem is easy to solve.\n",
